{"tid":1488423,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你個P牌仔又喺到帶風向","createTime":"2019-08-19T15:21:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T15:51:38.000Z","uid":276204,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"75c24964425fab97ac0f4275c3ea5053b95bca79","tid":1488423,"uid":276204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T15:21:26.000Z","msg":"無錯 個P牌就喺我 仲要第一次出post 我知實比人屌<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>但我寧願大家入嚟屌柒我 都唔想你地再討論大波黑警</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n尋日淋左幾粒鐘雨 今日發燒發到依家暈下暈下 訓左成日起身碌電話 見到好多人仲share緊隻大波狗乸嘅相 無論你喺J緊佢對波 定笑緊佢喺整容膠<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">呢隻黑狗乸都冇任何討論價值！！！！！</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n對波點大佢都喺一個<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警</span></span></strong> <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>香港警察冇一個喺無辜</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家<br />\n喺咪唔記得<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>黑警</strong></span></span>點對<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">700幾位被捕嘅手足義士們</span></strong></span><br />\n喺咪唔記得<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>五大訴求</strong></span></span>一樣都未成功<br />\n喺咪唔記得仲訓喺醫院受緊苦嘅<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">爆眼女義士</span></strong></span><br />\n喺咪唔記得咁多位<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">以死言諫嘅義士</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n明白大家都需要放鬆下 但已經講左成晚 求下唔好再討論同share佢啲相 唔好再follow佢ig <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>專注番嚟緊嘅抗爭活動</strong></span></span><br />\n我真喺好想好想有一日同大家喺煲低除罩相認  好想攬下所有同我一齊發過夢嘅手足 約實你地 我愛大家<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時大革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"eb2e8dac65715cf09c0307dc8118455b904741ce","tid":1488423,"uid":206827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T15:22:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔好意思 麻煩大家幫手投票定個死線<br />\n大家既訴求唔可以不了了之</span></span><br />\n死線投票<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1488382\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1488382</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5025331774802b7f8eab8d5ea0625e1736b47977","tid":1488423,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T15:25:21.000Z","msg":"（整合） 818之後仲有行動㗎我地！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1487938\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1487938</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"85be6d1449d7414fcec7037a14349b0a885b7c23","tid":1488423,"uid":276204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75c24964425fab97ac0f4275c3ea5053b95bca79","tid":1488423,"uid":276204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T15:21:26.000Z","msg":"無錯 個P牌就喺我 仲要第一次出post 我知實比人屌<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>但我寧願大家入嚟屌柒我 都唔想你地再討論大波黑警</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n尋日淋左幾粒鐘雨 今日發燒發到依家暈下暈下 訓左成日起身碌電話 見到好多人仲share緊隻大波狗乸嘅相 無論你喺J緊佢對波 定笑緊佢喺整容膠<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">呢隻黑狗乸都冇任何討論價值！！！！！</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" cl